{"ja442:0.1":"Jataka ","ja442:0.2":"Dasakanipata ","ja442:0.3":"Catudvaravagga ","ja442:0.4":"4. Sankhajataka ","ja442:1.1":"“Bahussuto sutadhammosi sankha, ","ja442:1.2":"Dittha taya samanabrahmana ca; ","ja442:1.3":"Athakkhane dassayase vilapam, ","ja442:1.4":"Anno nu ko te patimantako maya”. ","ja442:2.1":"“Subbhu subha suppatimukkakambu, ","ja442:2.2":"Paggayha sovannamayaya patiya; ","ja442:2.3":"‘Bhunjassu bhattam’ iti mam vadeti, ","ja442:2.4":"Saddhavitta ","ja442:2.5":"Tamaham noti brumi”. ","ja442:3.1":"“Etadisam brahmana disvana yakkham, ","ja442:3.2":"Puccheyya poso sukhamasisano; ","ja442:3.3":"Utthehi nam panjalikabhipuccha, ","ja442:3.4":"Devi nusi tvam uda manusi nu”. ","ja442:4.1":"“Yam tvam sukhenabhisamekkhase mam, ","ja442:4.2":"Bhunjassu bhattam iti mam vadesi; ","ja442:4.3":"Pucchami tam nari mahanubhave, ","ja442:4.4":"Devi nusi tvam uda manusi nu”. ","ja442:5.1":"“Devi aham sankha mahanubhava, ","ja442:5.2":"Idhagata sagaravarimajjhe; ","ja442:5.3":"Anukampika no ca padutthacitta, ","ja442:5.4":"Taveva atthaya idhagatasmi. ","ja442:6.1":"Idhannapanam sayanasananca, ","ja442:6.2":"Yanani nanavividhani sankha; ","ja442:6.3":"Sabbassa tyaham patipadayami, ","ja442:6.4":"Yam kinci tuyham manasabhipatthitam”. ","ja442:7.1":"“Yam kinci yitthanca hutanca mayham, ","ja442:7.2":"Sabbassa no issara tvam sugatte; ","ja442:7.3":"Susoni subbhamu suvilaggamajjhe, ","ja442:7.4":"Kissa me kammassa ayam vipako”. ","ja442:8.1":"“Ghamme pathe brahmana ekabhikkhum, ","ja442:8.2":"Ugghattapadam tasitam kilantam; ","ja442:8.3":"Patipadayi sankha upahanani, ","ja442:8.4":"Sa dakkhina kamaduha tavajja”. ","ja442:9.1":"“Sa hotu nava phalakupapanna, ","ja442:9.2":"Anavassuta erakavatayutta; ","ja442:9.3":"Annassa yanassa na hettha bhumi, ","ja442:9.4":"Ajjeva mam molinim papayassu”. ","ja442:10.1":"“Sa tattha vitta sumana patita, ","ja442:10.2":"Navam sucittam abhinimminitva; ","ja442:10.3":"Adaya sankham purisena saddhim, ","ja442:10.4":"Upanayi nagaram sadhuramman”ti. ","ja442:11.1":"Sankhajatakam catuttham. "}